   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click on the<uicontrol> Link</uicontrol> in the email you have received.</p>
            <stepresult>You are directed to the Welcome page of RFQ.</stepresult>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>View Survey</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the price and price modifiers.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To upload an attachment, click <uicontrol>Upload</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Choose File</uicontrol> ansd select the file that you want to
               upload. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the <uicontrol>File Name</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Attach</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>After you have entered all the responses, click <uicontrol>Submit</uicontrol>.You
               will be redirected to Thank you page.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>You can respond to the RFQ only once. Once you click Submit, you will not able
                     to edit or resend the responses of RFQ. If you try to click the link in your
                     email after you have responded to RFQ, you will be redirected to Thank you
                     page.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
